{"word":"G1263 - διαμαρτύρομαι - diamartýromai - dee-am-ar-too'-rom-ahee - Charge","slug":"G1263","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαμαρτύρομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>diamartýromai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>dee-am-ar-too'-rom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Charge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B4;&#x03B9;&#x03B1;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03C4;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - diamarturomai</b> - <i>dee-am-ar-too'-rom-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G3140\">G3140</a>; to <i>attest</i> or <i>protest earnestly</i>, or (by implication) <i>hortatively:</i> - charge, testify (unto), witness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1957\">G1957</a>, <a href=\"#/G2649\">G2649</a>, <a href=\"#/G3140\">G3140</a>, <a href=\"#/G3141\">G3141</a>, <a href=\"#/G3142\">G3142</a>, <a href=\"#/G3143\">G3143</a>, <a href=\"#/G3144\">G3144</a>, <a href=\"#/G4303\">G4303</a>, <a href=\"#/G4828\">G4828</a>, <a href=\"#/G4901\">G4901</a>, <a href=\"#/G5575\">G5575</a>, <a href=\"#/G5576\">G5576</a>, <a href=\"#/G5577\">G5577</a>"}]}